body.value:
Dear Candidates,

As every one knows that, Prelim is very much competitive in nature considering its rejection nature. Success rate of the pre is near about 1%. To clear the prelim, one must go through Exam environment, solve as much as Prelim tests. This will help you in two ways. 

1. To understand and acclamatise with exam enviroment, i.e. solve 100 questions in 2 hours, time management, how to choose questions, keep five minutes for review etc.

2. Practice of prelims questions give you focus areas where you want to concentrate. Since we choose the topics based on vast experience of our facultis and candidates who got selected. Every prelim question will give you insights and thought process to understand how questions are framed, how to study subjects, what is important things you need to know etc.

We have Online as well as Offline test series. We request you all to take opportunity and solve our quality test series which will give you overall birds eye view to tacle Prelim 2018.

Please find detailed plan of test series for offline and online test series. Interested candidates please connect or message here.
